碌鳩"},{"pid":"27f8ea677d623073f681730f43207b509272d01c","tid":2371120,"uid":9812,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T05:11:53.000Z","msg":"2008年<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">1月27日</span></span>，匿名網友於香港論壇的成人貼圖區內發布一幅色情相片。相中男子貌似藝人陳冠希，而女子則貌似藝人鍾欣桐。"},{"pid":"4860bfe2f67c91fb7117c87152565c590983ad5e","tid":2371120,"uid":181651,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T05:13:07.000Z","msg":"移花接木"},{"pid":"1d442d44042f55cb4af82ebf9a7c334e139cdbb6","tid":2371120,"uid":127347,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T05:14:00.000Z","msg":"一年容易又..."},{"pid":"10192ed481fd07d88df78c21364698f005e3fb5b","tid":2371120,"uid":271397,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T05:14:16.000Z","msg":"好掛住當時拜年問親戚朋友有冇睇咸相嘅經歷"},{"pid":"9c6eb305f850013408e85ee940803542eede867b","tid":2371120,"uid":192189,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T05:14:37.000Z","msg":"又真係幾震撼 <br />\n仲咁岩新年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />個個講"},{"pid":"2588c4c0c0c6e09105f6d8cbb5a4e44a885986cc","tid":2371120,"uid":48161,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T05:15:15.000Z","msg":"IVE個高級講師俾人炒未?"},{"pid":"ab2fc5330c071f25ab8b8c415b2b3ed6ef7c93be","tid":2371120,"uid":194120,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T05:16:29.000Z","msg":"冠希哥係男人嘅偶像"},{"pid":"d920c7b95523d28372ac89f621417a3a2a8dfb00","tid":2371120,"uid":33868,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T05:17:15.000Z","msg":"蘋果頭版呢"},{"pid":"1223c26551eeb7bca5632f063165914b51dfda9f","tid":2371120,"uid":34241,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T05:20:26.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>年</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"476018c6ec9c0c34f7f35ad8d99dae4674212e40","tid":2371120,"uid":39710,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T05:25:12.000Z","msg":"成疊慾照閃卡 我袋住拜年<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05cbb81c17080c483927d42d19a9bb1a4ce61c3c","tid":2371120,"uid":25560,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"476018c6ec9c0c34f7f35ad8d99dae4674212e40","tid":2371120,"uid":39710,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T05:25:12.000Z","msg":"成疊慾照閃卡 我袋住拜年<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T05:26:10.000Z","msg":"叫佢哋原班人馬再拍"},{"pid":"4b59e5cac9809a576cf18b67d8a316d7bec3016f","tid":2371120,"uid":167732,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T05:29:03.000Z","msg":"記得當年好好心咁俾啲搵唔到嘅同學仔睇<br />\n點知揚撚咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5c31a699df29e5ca3a2772189eb6ccee8a1edd7","tid":2371120,"uid":10757,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T05:29:19.000Z","msg":"柏G做老母 點過新年好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20e5583cb3aa94f7ab0da38e425b8ac0b083c29c","tid":2371120,"uid":60145,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T05:31:10.000Z","msg":"品味去了哪裏"},{"pid":"6207f7110950a44b2daa1d2beb91b2b6c6af04c7","tid":2371120,"uid":68860,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T05:34:37.000Z","msg":"做藝人難，在電子科技氾濫年代，做女藝人更難！互聯網前晚開始流傳兩張極度不雅的色情照片，當中包括疑似TWINS女歌手鍾欣桐（阿嬌），以及近年淡出歌壇的陳文媛。鍾欣桐所屬的英皇娛樂集團對事件感到憤怒，斥有人以電腦圖片<span class=\"red\">移花接木</span>手法，製作色情照片，是任何人都不能容忍的，予以極力譴責，並已向警方報案。<br />\n<br />\n互聯網討論區前日出現兩張色情照片，驟眼看來與鍾欣桐和陳文媛十分相似，兩張照片中的兩名女子均與疑似藝人陳冠希有猥褻的行為，其中貌似「阿嬌」者躺在脇上，張開雙腳，圖片左上角出現一名男子，貌似藝人陳冠希。另一圖片則是「陳文媛」和「陳冠希」，正在發生性行為，<span class=\"red\">但明眼人一看，已斷定是經移花接木製作的圖片</span>。 <br />\n<br />\n阿嬌經理人霍汶希表示，阿嬌已知道事件，感到很不開心，但沒有任何激動，亦不打算回應。霍汶希謂，阿嬌昨日原安排錄音，晚上到紅館看容祖兒演唱會，但事後已取消行程。 英皇娛樂集團對事件十分憤怒，藝人管理部發出嚴正聲明，指情況嚴重，公司會追查照片發放來源、發放人及上載人身份，並指任何人應立即停止發放、上載，或者刊登有關照片，不排除會作法律追究。 事件中受害人之一的男藝人陳冠希，昨晚透過胡關李羅律師行發出聲明，強烈指責該等不負責任的惡作劇行為，他保留一切追究法律責任的權利。 警方證實，昨晨接獲一名女子報案，指在網上發現一些有關其公司旗下職員的合成照片，事件已交由警方跟進。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0pfKRUn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0pfKRUn.jpg&h=36df3b6e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ffeecf272428b88df39ee04403b59f48148793af","tid":2371120,"uid":243756,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T05:37:00.000Z","msg":"一講起黑鮑 腦海好自然諗起佢個樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9b0524e2560520f44d94ec5922d97639843e72a","tid":2371120,"uid":223614,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ffeecf272428b88df39ee04403b59f48148793af","tid":2371120,"uid":243756,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T05:37:00.000Z","msg":"一講起黑鮑 腦海好自然諗起佢個樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T10:11:30.000Z","msg":"漢堡神偷<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2448add848267e7bb150fc2dabec35dd0e48c182","tid":2371120,"uid":25379,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T10:32:47.000Z","msg":"阿嬌都被人搞到精神病<br />\n成世無咗㗎喇<br />\n放過下人啦"},{"pid":"a005ea8cae7ccdb572262ec3c19b9676e27908a5","tid":2371120,"uid":111006,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T11:49:11.000Z","msg":"有冇人知呢本野而家值幾錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HrBTwY8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHrBTwY8.png&h=08183a03&s={SIZE}\" /><p class=\"left\"></p>"}]}